      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2008 Corvette Z06 featuring the legendary LS7 7.0L V8. This powerhouse utilizes a dry-sump oiling system and titanium intake valves to deliver a linear power band up to its 7,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a rear-mounted Tremec TR6060 6-speed manual transaxle, optimized for weight distribution. The hydroformed aluminum chassis and magnesium engine cradle remain rigid, providing exceptional lateral grip. Recent service includes a comprehensive inspection of the valvetrain and cooling system. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its mileage, the performance envelope remains intact, offering a raw, analog driving experience.",
