      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior finish retains a deep, impressive gloss, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014standard signs of careful road use. Step inside to find a cabin that has been treated with respect; the leather seats are supple and free of any cracks or stains, and the dashboard remains pristine. Every button and switch works perfectly, including the heated seats, navigation system, and the power sunroof. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, backed by a complete service history that shows regular oil changes and timely preventative maintenance. The brakes are responsive, and the tires have approximately 70% of their tread remaining. This car drives straight and true, offering a quiet, composed ride that feels as solid today as it did when it first hit the road. It is a dependable, honest vehicle that is ready to be driven home today.",
